- reference appropriate schema files under backend/src/db/schema
- database queries should use the functions defined in [queryTimer.js](mdc:backend/src/db/queryTimer.js)
- use the timedQuery() function for database queries that do not require transaction support.
- use the runTransactionWith() function to run multiple queries wrapped in a transaction.